                    <div class="policy-section" id="information-collection">
                        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Personal information (name, email address, etc.) when you create an account</li>
                            <li>Course progress and completion data</li>
                            <li>Payment information when you make a purchase</li>
                            <li>Communications you send to us</li>
                            <li>Information about your device and internet connection</li>
                            <li>Usage data through cookies and similar technologies</li>
