                    </div>
    
                    <div class="policy-section" id="contact-us">
                        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
                        <p>Email: <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="c0b0b2a9b6a1a3b980b4b5b4afb2a9a1aca8b5a2eea9af">Helloworldinfo1@gmail.com</a></p>
